Type: Package
Package: taxref4R
Title: Get information from the French TAXREF API
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Cédric Mondy
Maintainer: Cédric Mondy <cedric.mondy@gmail.com>
Description: This packages brings functions to call different endpoints of
    the French TAXREF API. This API delivers information about species
    taxonomic details as well as information about their protection and
    conservation status.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Depends: 
    R (>= 2.10)
Imports: 
    dplyr,
    httr,
    jsonlite,
    purrr,
    rvest,
    tibble
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.1
